kit-preload-data=\"off\">\n\t\t<div style=\"display: contents\"><!--[--><!--[--><!----><div class=\"theme-black\" id=\"app\"><!--[--><!----><nav><a class=\"logo\" href=\"/\"><img src=\"/logo.svg\" alt=\"logo\" width=\"46\" height=\"30\"/></a><form role=\"search\" action=\"/search/\" class=\"search\"><input value=\"\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"e.g. stockings\" type=\"search\" autocapitalize=\"none\" autocomplete=\"off\" required/><!--[!--><!--]--><dialog class=\"save-dialog svelte-1kyqczv\"><h2 class=\"svelte-1kyqczv\">Save this search</h2> <p class=\"dialog-info svelte-1kyqczv\">Saved searches let you quickly re-run a query from the search bar dropdown. Up to 10 can be\n\t\tstored locally on this device.</p> <label class=\"svelte-1kyqczv\"><span class=\"svelte-1kyqczv\">Name (optional)</span> <input type=\"text\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"Leave blank to use the query\" maxlength=\"60\" class=\"svelte-1kyqczv\"/></label> <p class=\"dialog-query svelte-1kyqczv\"></p> <div class=\"dialog-actions svelte-1kyqczv\"><!--[!--><!--]--> <span class=\"spacer svelte-1kyqczv\"></span> <button type=\"button\" class=\"svelte-1kyqczv\">Cancel</button> <button type=\"button\" class=\"primary svelte-1kyqczv\">Save</button></div></dialog><!----><!--[!--><!--]--><!----><button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-square\" aria-label=\"Search\"><i class=\"fa fa-search fa-lg\"></i></button></form><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-square\" id=\"hamburger\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><span class=\"line\"></span><span class=\"line\"></span><span class=\"line\"></span></button><div class=\"collapse\"><ul class=\"menu left\"><li class=\"desktop  svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/random/\">Random</a></li><li class=\"desktop  svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/tags/\">Tags</a></li><li class=\"desktop  svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/artists/\">Artists</a></li><li class=\"desktop  svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/characters/\">Characters</a></li><li class=\"desktop  svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/parodies/\">Parodies</a></li><li class=\"desktop  svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/groups/\">Groups</a></li><li class=\"desktop community-menu svelte-1ml9nak\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"community-btn svelte-1ml9nak active\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Community <i class=\"fa fa-chevron-down community-caret svelte-1ml9nak\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></button><ul class=\"community-panel svelte-1ml9nak\"><li class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/community/taxonomy/\" class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\">Taxonomy</a></li><li class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/community/gts-backlog/\" class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\">GTS Backlog</a></li><li class=\"active svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/info/\" class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\">Info</a></li></ul></li><li class=\"desktop\"><a href=\"//tsyndicate.com/api/v1/direct/e220320bd2e542b8a2ab7cd2c5a9df8c?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">AI Sluts 😈</a></li><li class=\"desktop\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/nhentaiOfficial\" aria-label=\"Twitter\"><i class=\"fab fa-twitter fa-lg\"></i></a></li><li class=\"dropdown\"><button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-square\" type=\"button\" id=\"dropdown\" aria-label=\"More links\"><i class=\"fa fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><ul class=\"dropdown-menu\"><li class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/random/\">Random</a></li><li class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/tags/\">Tags</a></li><li class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/artists/\">Artists</a></li><li class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/characters/\">Characters</a></li><li class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/parodies/\">Parodies</a></li><li class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/groups/\">Groups</a></li><li class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/community/taxonomy/\">Taxonomy</a></li><li class=\"svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/community/gts-backlog/\">GTS Backlog</a></li><li class=\"active svelte-1ml9nak\"><a href=\"/info/\">Info</a></li><li><a href=\"//tsyndicate.com/api/v1/direct/e220320bd2e542b8a2ab7cd2c5a9df8c?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">AI Sluts😈</a></li><li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/nhentaiOfficial\" aria-label=\"Twitter\"><i class=\"fab fa-twitter fa-lg\"></i></a></li></ul></li></ul><ul class=\"menu right\"><!--[!--><li class=\"menu-sign-in\"><a href=\"/login/\"><i class=\"fa fa-sign-in-alt\"></i> Sign in</a></li><li class=\"menu-register\"><a href=\"/register/\"><i class=\"fa fa-edit\"></i> Register</a></li><!--]--></ul></div></nav><!----> <!--[!--><!--]--><!----> <div id=\"content\" style=\"padding-bottom: 1em;\"><!--[!--><!----><div class=\"container svelte-weo7t8\" id=\"info-container\"><section class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"><h2 class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Accessing nhentai</h2> <ul class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"><li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Official domain: <a href=\"https://nhentai.net\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">nhentai.net</a></li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Tor Onion: <a href=\"http://nhentaithbeuysdaiiqf6nkxey6qzlbtb5wlwheq22abjfehlzghtgid.onion/\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">nhentaithbeuysdaiiqf6nkxey6qzlbtb5wlwheq22abjfehlzghtgid.onion</a>.<br class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"/> <span style=\"font-size: .7em;\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">You <u class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">must</u> be inside the tor network. <a href=\"https://tb-manual.torproject.org/about/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Learn more</a>.</span></li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">More to come.</li></ul></section> <section class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"><h2 class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Accounts</h2> <ul class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"><li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Unlimited favorites.</li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Tag blacklisting.</li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Three gorgeous themes: light, blue, and black.</li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">API key access for developers.</li></ul></section> <section class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"><h2 class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Search</h2> <ul class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"><li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">You can search for multiple terms at the same time, and this will return only galleries that contain both terms. For example, <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">anal tanlines</code> finds all galleries that contain both <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">anal</code> and <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">tanlines</code>.</li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">You can exclude terms by prefixing them with <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">-</code>. For example, <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">anal tanlines -yaoi</code> matches all galleries matching <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">anal</code> and <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">tanlines</code> but not <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">yaoi</code>.</li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Exact searches can be performed by wrapping terms in double quotes. For example, <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">\"big breasts\"</code> only matches galleries with \"big breasts\" somewhere in the title or in tags.</li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">These can be combined with tag namespaces for finer control over the query: <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">parodies:railgun -tag:\"big breasts\"</code>.</li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">You can search for galleries with a specific number of pages with <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">pages:20</code>, or with a page range: <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">pages:>20 pages:&lt;=30</code>.</li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">You can search for galleries uploaded within some timeframe with <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">uploaded:20d</code>. Valid units are <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">h</code>, <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">d</code>, <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">w</code>, <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">m</code>, <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">y</code>. You can use ranges as well: <code class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">uploaded:>20d uploaded:&lt;30d</code>.</li></ul></section> <section class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"><h2 class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">API</h2> <ul class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"><li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">API documentation is available at <a href=\"/api/v2/docs\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">/api/v2/docs</a>.</li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Generate API keys in your <a href=\"/login/\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">account settings</a> to access the API programmatically.</li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Have a cool project that needs higher rate limits? Tell us about it at <a href=\"mailto:support@nhentai.net\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">support@nhentai.net</a>.</li></ul></section> <section id=\"pow\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"><h2 class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Anti-Spam Challenges</h2> <ul class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"><li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Some areas of the site are protected by a short cryptographic puzzle your browser solves automatically.</li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">This helps deter some automated spam without requiring invasive tracking or third-party services.</li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">It typically takes a few seconds on modern devices but may take longer on older hardware.</li></ul></section> <section class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"><h2 class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Want to get in touch?</h2> <ul class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"><li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">General Inquiries: <a href=\"mailto:hey@nhentai.net\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">hey@nhentai.net</a></li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Support: <a href=\"mailto:support@nhentai.net\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">support@nhentai.net</a></li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Abuse: <a href=\"mailto:abuse@nhentai.net\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">abuse@nhentai.net</a></li> <li class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nhentaiOfficial\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">@nhentaiOfficial</a></li></ul></section> <section id=\"thanks\" class=\"svelte-weo7t8\">Thanks for supporting the site! <br class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"/> <i class=\"fa fa-heart color-icon svelte-weo7t8\"></i> Love, <br class=\"svelte-weo7t8\"/> –Team nhentai</section></div><!----><!--]--><!----></div><!----><!--]--><!----></div> <!--[!--><!--]--><!----><!----><!--]--> <!--[!--><!--]--><!--]-->\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<script>\n\t\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\t\t__sveltekit_ccts5f = {\n\t\t\t\t\t\tbase: new URL(\".\", location).pathname.slice(0, -1)\n\t\t\t\t\t};\n\n\t\t\t\t\tconst 